CBRE is pleased to offer to the market for sale, one of the most anticipated blocks of B5 zoned land in Western Sydney.

The site benefits from the below features:

+ DA approved for a 50 unit industrial/office estate.
+ Total site area: 19,700 sqm
+ 18,300 sqm of developable area.
+ Approved GLA 12,500 sqm
+ Flexible B5 zoning
+ Huge frontage to Horsley Drive of 186 metres.
+ Shovel ready project

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: PRIME INDUSTRIAL LAND IN WESTERN SYDNEY | DA APPROVED 50 UNIT INDUSTRIAL ESTATE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
- Access via one (1) x on-grade roller shutter door 
- Internal clearances ranging from 6.1 – 8.0 metres*
- Ample power supply available 
- Mezzanine level office - tiled and air-conditioned
- Male & female amenities
- Security fenced site + concrete yard
- Six (6) Allocated car parking spaces
- Zoned IN1 General Industrial 

Please contact the exclusive agent for further information.

For Sale by EOI

CBRE is pleased to offer to the market via expressions of interest campaign, two of the most highly sought after blocks of B5 zoned land in Western Sydney.

+ Opportunity to purchase individually or together in one line
+ Lot 921: 7,860 sqm*
+ Lot 922: 6,057 sqm*
+ Total Area; 13,917sqm*

Both sites are for sale by expression of interest closing Thursday March the 18th at 4 pm.

Please contact the exclusive agent Elijah Shakir from CBRE for a full information pack and contract of sale.
